      "role": "user",
      "content": "Negative. The power deficit is too critical to permit any additional non-essential cycles. The diagnostic run is not authorized. We need to preserve the remaining battery capacity specifically for the final data downlink. \n\nProceed with the shutdown sequence preparation immediately. Confirm you are ready to enter the low-power state.",
